The article is a transcript of a conversation between the President and reporters. The reporters asked the President when he plans to announce his reelection, to which he responded that he will announce it when he is ready. They also asked if he plans to visit Ohio to discuss a train derailment and federal assistance. The President replied that he has been in contact with officials from Ohio and Pennsylvania and has laid out his thoughts on the situation. He mentioned that legislation will be implemented and he will visit Ohio at some point. The conversation took place at 2:19 PM EST.